data.description: Are you looking for space in the heart of the City of Fairmont?  Here is your chance!  This home has invited you into its spacious kitchen open to the dining area.  Main floor laundry and full bath.  The primary bedroom has the deck out the patio doors perfect for that morning cup of Joe or a nightly beverage of your choice.   Upstairs you will find 3 more bedrooms and a full bath.  There is a stairwell to the attic also.  Lower level you have so much space with another bedroom, family room and rec room.  No basement issues in this beauty!  3 yes I said 3 levels of living space with maintenance free siding.  Newer concrete driveway, ADT system, Ring doorbells and numerous other updates.  This all can be yours~set up your private tour today!!
